1. *On je proverio* da li su svi zadaci završeni. (He checked whether all tasks were finished.) 
2. *Proverili* smo sve informacije. (We checked all the information.) 
3. *Provera* je bila jako ozbiljna. (The check was very serious.) 
4. *Proveravamo* sve moguće opcije. (We are checking all possible options.) 
5. *Provereno* je da je sve ispravno. (It was verified that everything was correct.) 
6. *Proveravala* je neke stvari. (She was checking some things.)